
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "主页";
    Layout = "~/Areas/Product/Views/Shared/Product/_LayoutKotoriTech.cshtml";
}

<!--自己的css-->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/Content/_MyContent/About/Emphasize.css"/>
<script>
    $("#MenuHome").addClass("active");
</script>
<div class="Text">
    <img src="/Areas/Product/Content/Image/Icon/KotoriTech.jpg" alt="Icon" height="150" width="450" />
    <br />
    <h3>KotoriTech简介</h3>
    <hr />
    <p>KotoriTech是由Nulla小组组长@(MemberUri.GetMemberUri(Html, Administrator.小鸟小姐))开发制作的Minecraft Mod，面向Minecraft 1.7.10，基于Forge API和IndustrialCraft。</p>
    <p>组长似乎是认为原版IndustrialCraft过于简单，因此<del>计划</del>增加大量与现实生活比较相似的特性，也集合了一些之前就有的脑洞，以使IC玩家感到更加<del>抖M</del>好玩。</p>
    <p>出于对另一IC2扩展的致敬<del>其实是两个管理员强烈要求</del>，组长将此mod命名为Kotori Tech。</p>
    <p class="emphasize">本mod基于Forge 10.13.4.1614及以上版本。</p>
    <p>@Html.ActionLink("<<去往下载页", "Download", "Home", new { area = "Product", modname = "KotoriTech" }, null)</p>
    <p>@Html.ActionLink("<<去往图库页", "Image", "Home", new { area = "Product", modname = "KotoriTech" }, null)</p>
</div>

